== English ==

=== Noun ===
{{wikipedia}}
'''pomelo'''
#A large yellow [[citrus]] fruit native to southeastern [[Asia]] and [[Malaysia]]. It has a sweet flesh and is about 25 [[centimeter|centimeters]] in [[diameter]].

=== Other Names ===
The pomelo is also commonly known as:

*pummelo

*pommelo

*jabong

*shaddock

